{
  "stem": "1721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 272.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, this was just related to me by the person who interviewed me for that first tape-- called me a few years later.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was somewhat amazed when a colleague of hers called her from the east coast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they communicate on a regular basis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they probably discuss certain aspects of stories coming from the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so that came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so she remembered my explanation of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she called me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was kind of-- kind of vindicated because you sometimes wonder, you know, did I see it someplace?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or did I read it or something?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or was it a dream or not, so-- It sounds like it would be more of a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah, I don't-- you know, I can't drudge up the same emotions I felt at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't really recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm certain, being seven or eight years old, I'm sure I wasn't very comfortable, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think there was very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other than those few isolated instances, I don't really recall anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Consciously, I don't really recall very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure what I would recall if I were to be put on Demerol or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think I suffered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Personally, I don't think I suffered a lot of tragedies, which would force me to suppress information.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was probably just childhood, you know, memory lapses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, that may be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think my mother prepared me for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I did not come from a very loving home where there was a lot of Judaism, and where I was pulled away from my family and separated.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
